<p><strong>翻译：</strong><a href="http://www.scp-wiki.net/elysium">点此查看主站发布版</a>，感谢<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/sunnyclockwork" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1621343); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1621343&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1606663817" alt="SunnyClockwork" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1621343)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/sunnyclockwork" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1621343); return false;">SunnyClockwork</a></span>翻译！！<span style="color: transparent">Infas12心脏已停跳</span></p>
<p><strong>背景相关：</strong>本故事为设定中心linkage下的麦克斯韦宗相关内容。<a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/linkage-hub">点此查看中心页。</a></p>
</div>
<hr />
<div class="credit-back" style="text-align: center;">
<p><iframe src="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/credit:backmodule/code/2" align="" frameborder="" height="" scrolling="no" width="" class="" style="height:2em;width: 100%;margin: 0;padding: 0;border: 0;background: transparent;"></iframe></p>
